&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance: &lt;/strong&gt;Ensure every deal meets lender guidelines, state regulations, and internal compliance standards. Deal-level compliance is non-negotiable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leading Indicators: &lt;/strong&gt;Monitor funding time, deal kickbacks, and stipulation clearance rates as the primary health signals for F&amp;amp;I operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capacity &amp;amp; Structure: &lt;/strong&gt;Identify constraints in F&amp;amp;I staffing or role definition and escalate to the VP of Operations before they affect throughput.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
