&lt;p&gt;As a Parts Specialist, you will be the cornerstone of our vehicle reconditioning process, responsible for the efficient and accurate management of all automotive parts inventory. This is an on-site role, based in our Orange County (Irvine) operations center. You will ensure our technicians have the right parts at the right time to keep our reconditioning turnaround times fast and our quality standards high. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
