&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DMV Liaison: &lt;/strong&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for DMV inquiries, rejections, and resubmissions. Resolve errors quickly to protect funding timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Temp Tags &amp;amp; Plate Fulfillment: &lt;/strong&gt;Issue temporary permits accurately and manage timely fulfillment of permanent plates and registration documents to customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EV Incentive Documentation: &lt;/strong&gt;Support customers with state-specific EV registration incentive documentation (e.g., HOV sticker eligibility, clean vehicle rebate forms) where applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
